## hostname: cb-xserve04.mozilla.com
## uname: Darwin cb-xserve04.mozilla.com 9.8.0 Darwin Kernel Version 9.8.0: Wed Jul 15 16:55:01 PDT 2009; root:xnu-1228.15.4~1/RELEASE_I386 i386
